    <!-- Page Content -->
    <a  name="services"></a>
    <div class="content-section-a">

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h3 class="section-heading">Protect your cards today</h3>
                    <p class="lead">
                        By loading images of your cards into your Vault, you secure them today against future high quality counterfeits. <br><br>
                        In the future, when purchasing or trading a card, you will also get or give the digital history record of the card, proving that it existed before undetectable counterfeits, and therefore guarantying its value and genuinity.<br><br>
                        The clock is ticking, take action today and guarantee the future value of your cards.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="spacebox70"> </div>
                    <%= image_tag("landing1.png", :alt => "rss feed", class: "img-responsive") %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->
    </div>
    <!-- /.content-section-a -->

    <div class="content-section-b">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 col-sm-push-6  col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h3 class="section-heading">Build card history</h3>
                    <p class="lead">
                        Once a card is registered, modifications as well as ownership changes are registered in the system, building a traceability of the card origin.<br><br>
                        These records help build confidence and security in the community.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-pull-6  col-sm-6">
                    <div class="spacebox70"> </div>
                    <%= image_tag("landing2.png", :alt => "rss feed", class: "img-responsive") %>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->
    </div>
    <!-- /.content-section-b -->

    <div class="content-section-c">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h3 class="section-heading">Ask Experts to check if some cards are counterfeits</h3>
                    <p class="lead">
                        We have built an additional community check system, in which you can try to contact Experts to check either the real card or sometimes HD pictures of it and try to detect counterfeits. <br><br>
                        Having an Expert validation of your cards does not fully guarantee they are genuine, but adds a layer of trust and protection of your assets.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="spacebox70"> </div>
                    <%= image_tag("landing3.png", :alt => "rss feed", class: "img-responsive") %>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->
    </div>
    <!-- /.content-section-c -->

    <div class="content-section-d">
        <div class="container">
