                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h3 class="section-heading">Insure your cards</h3>
                    <p class="lead">
                        We are working on allowing users to ensure the content of their Vault against theft or destruction. This would protect collectors or players when valuables are lost or destroyed, assessing of the previous ownership. <br><br>
                        This service is not operational yet, stay tuned!
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-pull-6  col-sm-6">
                    <div class="spacebox70"> </div>
                    <%= image_tag("landing4.png", :alt => "rss feed", class: "img-responsive") %>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
